Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Free speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about having compassion for being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I notice that I have a lot of, like, self-judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a feeling, not like thoughts happen, but it's just sort of a,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I notice there's some deep-seated self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And a fear of making mistakes, just a lot of judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel, like, inside, I feel like that compassion is there towards myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I can feel it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I can taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just not, like, there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, it's not, you know, a part of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just want to be okay with being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Be okay to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be okay with being human and making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, hatred is excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we all realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A decent regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A decent regret is what's appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you ran over six people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You burned down their house and caused them to go bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's required is a decent regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that other people are also at the effect of their karma as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't take on omnipotence to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the cause of that or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have had a participatory involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're only a participant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a determiner of outcomes, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you forgive yourself for just being more limited than you might think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You put in your two cents worth, but that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the momentum of a person's life is what's running them 90% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Their life is in a spin to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you got in their life, and then after you left, their life got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, oh, look what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in a free fall to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to get involved with scrupulosity, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have kindness and forgiveness towards yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a wrinkle cloth here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are these all coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first, I just want to say I love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak about disidentification with the mind, ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw you in August.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And since that time, I've had a better perception of disidentification with thoughts and mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't identify them as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is an it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you understand the mind's an it, stop calling it me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you can say, it is screwed up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I, however, am pure and innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's been an experience of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there's a trigger, so for instance, the other day on the phone, there was a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got triggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seemed as though I went from, like I was forced back into my body almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I felt it in my solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I went from that state of being able to witness to being the-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, spiritual progression is erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And well, you know, no, no, you wasn't in that bad a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You got fractured out of a good space, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My immediate response was to try to, well, not try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My immediate response was forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You put your thumb and middle finger together, both sides, and think the sound ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of divinity, I am forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of divinity, I am forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold the thumb and the middle finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound the sound ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Think ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Think, think, think ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Think ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's now clear, is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You just cleared that negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to, like, clear the aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's another way, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is om even better than ah, silently?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do the thymic thump.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do them all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think the sound ah, sound the sound om, om, hold these together, and then thump the thymus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, you've forgotten what the hell you were feeling guilty about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, may I just have a blessing that I can maintain that as long as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can maintain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He was detached and became undetached.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, could you help me, um, ah, with the, ah, some Luciferic temptations, like, um, love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is a constraint or limitation to freedom, or pride and power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to translate what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, like, how to protect oneself, or to deal with the Luciferic temptations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How to protect yourself, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect yourself against Luciferic temptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That love is a constraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I already explained several methods, and, ah, traditionally, also, people burn incense,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and, ah, smudge the room, ah, mantras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What negativity is going to dare come near you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking more of temptations that come from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Temptations that come from more inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, um, that love is a constraint to freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a constraint to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From a demonic entity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The correct translation of that is, is attachment is a deterrent to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the royal road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The way of the heart is the royal road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity and love are not two distinct things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a quality of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Attachment, however, is what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither attachments nor aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Doc, how do you know when you have an attachment to love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're not worried about it, you probably don't have an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's feeling that you'll die without the other person, that you don't want to go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that your life is over and ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made them the be-all and end-all of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And lost sense of your own sense of self.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can you tell the difference between romantic love and unconditional love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love, you love the person no matter what they do or whether they stay with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you or they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Conditional love, they only stay with you, I mean, you love them if they stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of times, it's a combination of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some real love, also some attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Biologic forces are very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The survival of the race, you know, depends on biologic drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you can't just do a outro, because if it wasn't for biologic drives, you wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,be here to complain about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Yes, indeed. That's all right. It's okay. Uh-huh. Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:12:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins. Hello. Hello, Susan. As always, I'm compelled to give my heartfelt thanks and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,gratitude to you for your dedication to your students. Your dedication to us profoundly moves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,me, and I'm deeply grateful. And to you as well, Susan. Your devotion to Dr. Hawkins is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,deeply admirable, and we love you for that, too. We love you, Dr. Hawkins. Thank you. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,welcome. My question today is about you make reference to certain truths that humanity can't
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,handle, that are results of your research, that are not published.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And I was wondering if you would consider
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,making some of those, some of that information available when you feel-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the public can't handle? You want me to make it public?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To those of us who might be able to handle it. I just feel that there's-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you do your own investigation, you'll run across things that cannot really, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,theoretically could be shared, but pragmatically speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,things that's written is not fit to print, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it also requires discretion, who and where to share certain things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's whole segments of society that are totally built on falsehood. Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing is completely fallacious. The whole industry is based on a fallacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Scientific endeavors, multi-billion dollar research projects, which I can tell you the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,outcome of the research project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,about 10 billion dollars ahead of where I know it's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's credibility, you know, all things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Logos, ethos, and pathos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Logos is the wisdom of the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethos is the caliber of the communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And pathos is the receptivity of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't ignore any one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have an authentic message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be authentically presented.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you have to have discernment about the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's certain things that you cannot tell people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or you could only tell them under different circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,under a different relationship, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're not ready to handle it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a subtlety.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Any situation requires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the patient walks in the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've made an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know about 90% of what ails them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to tell them now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe six months from now, when they've developed trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and when many of the things have turned out to be helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've taught them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And then would be the right time, so you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I trust you're knowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And the means is correct, but the timing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's lots of things we could put in the books
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that would blow the scarf off people's ears, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to read that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a post-mortem book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Post-mortem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I kind of assumed that, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I trust your judgment to always reveal to us what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because you're responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for the whole phenomena, all three phases,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what they can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the truth is really truthful,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:16:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you can express it in a way that is, you know, correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're deeply grateful for the truth that you do reveal to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I ask for your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mentioned some things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that people don't know the answers to, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The secrets of some of the most traditional mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was Jack the Ripper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to Amelia Earhart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who stole the Lindbergh baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, stuff that goes on in the press decade after decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find out the answer to all those things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in about two minutes flat, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I've just recently been introduced to your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am deeply honored to be in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be up here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, as an actor, if I assume the role of a,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a villain, is there any karmic consequence to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it may depend on karmic propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some risk in assuming the role of a villain, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As an actor, he is safe from any negative effects
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of playing the role of a negative person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess as an actor, you are protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's because it's a craft skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like in surgery, you cut somebody, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not guilty of laceration because you're doing surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see your consternation about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,though I'd probably give it a thought myself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, and I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a craft, but I could see his concern
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't know what kind of entities you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to pull into the field, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The symphony in red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So good to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I come to give you an update on my daughter's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the six months that we've been introduced to your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we've followed everything that you have suggested in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,taking her off of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I found an integrous psychiatrist that finally believed me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that didn't want to lock us both up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And she understands that the antipsychotic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that she gave my daughter, it started out at two milligrams,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but she could still hear the demons talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't tried to kill herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and she hasn't tried to kill me again, so that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we're at five milligrams, and the voices stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She stopped hearing the voices, but she's still having seizures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the seizures have worsened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So now what I do, when she goes into one, I can almost intuit that it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to happen, and I put my hand on her back, and I say the prayer to refuse and rebuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet it's still coming, and now I'm hearing music in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hearing music?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So why am I hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I can feel them touch me when it's at its worst, but what is this music?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if I go to the doctor and tell them I'm hearing music, they're going to want to lock me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to want to lock us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We have permission to ask about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This one here has a brain disorder of a minimal degree, which one has a more maximal degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So it's congenital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a minimal degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an aberration of neurological functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessarily pathologic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a variation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can quell it if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Orthomolecular psychiatry suggested various nutritional means of altering the brain chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,by introducing larger doses of vitamin B3 and vitamin C,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which by mass action then tend to throw brain chemistry into a different area,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,less likely to produce those kinds of neurologic effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just a neurophysiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's various ways you can change it experimentally, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture, there's a very, nutrition and acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And with academic medicine, you're already doing what you can do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No seizure, how do I address the seizures?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I put her back on seizure meds?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I take her to a neurologist?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's at 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she get the seizure meds to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The quacks at Mayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The quacks at Mayo in Rochester, Minnesota.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mayo Clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mayo Clinic is where she got the seizure meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would just, why don't you just continue it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Put her back on some of it that test out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethoxymide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethoxymide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a neurologist or psychiatrist now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have both.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They should certainly be able to answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And anti-seizure medication should bring about improvement, you know, with no downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't worked yet, but I have faith that it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the antipsychotic, it's at such a high dose that it makes her sleepy and unable to go to school or function.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I had hoped to do is just maybe take her back down to the five milligrams of the antipsychotic and then not so much like, it's not doping.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not doping her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All clinical work is trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're dealing with likelihoods and balance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much, you get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Too little, the symptoms come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's a variety of medications now in that class, so there's probably half
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a dozen things that would be helpful, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:23:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you try this, and then from that, the clinician guesses that this would probably
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,also be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe not make you so sleepy or something, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a matter of expertise in clinical psychopharmacology, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter is usually too scared to ask you a question, but she wrote one down, and she
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to hold Ms. Susan's hand while she asked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going too close to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I want to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm scared my dreams and my goals of this world will keep me from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Being involved in this world will keep you from enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first you have to master this world before you can leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd work on making yourself as successful as possible as you can within the worldly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,domain, and then worry about transcending it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't transcend it until you've mastered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.43,0:24:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So first, with practice, et cetera, try to become as expertise as you can in handling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you use psychopharmacology to compensate for any neurologic genetic things you've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.88,0:24:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just genetic and biochemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Genetic and biochemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of your help, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.52,0:24:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you are truly the only one that can help us, or even believes us, when we
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.52,0:24:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,tell them that we see these things, and it touches, and that she hears them, and she
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.52,0:24:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,hears them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.52,0:24:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly the only one that's believed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those are relatively common, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.52,0:24:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see large numbers of patients, you know, a certain percentage have these symptoms
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.52,0:24:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,fall into certain categories, you know, hearing or visual or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.52,0:24:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And with a little experimentation, you can usually find what works.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.63,0:25:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's brain chemistry is different, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.61,0:25:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But with experience, you can pretty much guess pretty often, you know, one milligram of prolific
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.61,0:25:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,does it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe two, three at the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.61,0:25:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everybody for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.97,0:25:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this took a little long.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.28,0:25:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.28,0:25:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you augment it with other things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You augment it with nutrition, diet, acupuncture, everything you think might be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.28,0:25:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.28,0:25:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You just hit it hammer and tongs, and it'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.48,0:25:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.48,0:25:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.48,0:25:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.48,0:25:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.48,0:25:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.75,0:25:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.00,0:25:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.39,0:25:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.44,0:25:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.44,0:25:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.44,0:25:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.45,0:25:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.45,0:25:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.45,0:25:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.45,0:25:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.45,0:25:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a case for experienced ..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.45,0:25:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.45,0:26:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to take a moment and look into your eyes and ask for the transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to transmit because there's no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I send you nothingness?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.25,0:26:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I send you nothingness?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.96,0:26:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Inferning in the auric field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.96,0:26:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.67,0:26:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetimes ago that I was with myself, 24, 25, a long time ago, almost to the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.11,0:26:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a six-year-old son who, from a very young age, I knew he was very open and received
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.79,0:26:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.25,0:26:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you speak slower and closer to the mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.57,0:26:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.38,0:26:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a six-year-old son.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.90,0:26:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.64,0:26:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.60,0:26:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And from a very young age, I knew that he was very open and very gifted in many senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.02,0:27:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's having a little bit of difficulty in school in the sense that he's a very active
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.36,0:27:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,child and very bright, and they're trying to peg him to be, you know, the normal public
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.93,0:27:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.78,0:27:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you could tell me something that would be able to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.50,0:27:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Help what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.76,0:27:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for him to adapt or...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.67,0:27:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.79,0:27:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bright and active.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.25,0:27:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.25,0:27:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.55,0:27:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what comes out?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.33,0:27:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.61,0:27:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.48,0:27:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to label him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, label him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.16,0:27:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just ADD or...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.03,0:27:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he has ADD.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.92,0:27:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.14,0:27:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Broken leg is not a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.64,0:27:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a broken leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.77,0:27:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost all of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.88,0:27:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.05,0:27:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost all of his sense of wanting to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.55,0:27:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels like there's a lot of negative attention instead of helping him in...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of negative attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.03,0:28:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, he's losing recess because he's wiggling around in his seat, because he needs to run
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.17,0:28:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.36,0:28:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.63,0:28:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being evasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.06,0:28:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his clinical diagnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.82,0:28:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ADHD?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.13,0:28:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had him tested with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.13,0:28:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he on any kind of treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.54,0:28:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.44,0:28:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.75,0:28:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher says he's hyperactive?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.68,0:28:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and so he wiggles around in his seat, so then she restricts him from recess, which
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is what the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.57,0:28:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.94,0:28:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he able to desist at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.96,0:28:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.44,0:28:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he has no...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.00,0:28:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to have any control of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.59,0:28:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wants to move all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.16,0:28:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he just wants to move all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.40,0:28:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you need to have him tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.01,0:28:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he probably has just ADD or ADHD, which is a very simple thing to cure, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.50,0:28:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to cure it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.11,0:28:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About three and a half minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.36,0:29:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.97,0:29:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.58,0:29:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And see if he calms down.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.67,0:29:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.08,0:29:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The caffeine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.13,0:29:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's due to...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.02,0:29:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The caffeine reacts differently to...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.34,0:29:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the human body is normally like this all the time, and the prefrontal cortex, right
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.52,0:29:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of this corona, there's a section of the brain, its function is to suppress.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.02,0:29:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.39,0:29:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the prefrontal cortex is underactive, it allows the rest of the thing to constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.02,0:29:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,go, like a chicken with its head cut off runs wildly around, because you've cut off the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.58,0:29:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,suppressor strips.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.47,0:29:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess would be clinically, he's got a deficient function of the prefrontal cortex,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.03,0:29:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the suppressor strips are not suppressing hyperactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.96,0:29:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.44,0:29:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.79,0:29:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple, and there's nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.16,0:29:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a neurologic variant, and it's quite common.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.29,0:30:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, 5%, 10% of kids all have it, and a lot of them grow out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.24,0:30:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's also various nutritional approaches to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.48,0:30:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Untreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.96,0:30:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The side effects of untreating it are going to be worse than the illness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.29,0:30:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time you've been bad enough and been put in the naughty seat, enough time your
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.75,0:30:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,self-esteem is going to be zilch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.16,0:30:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would treat it early rather than go into denial and say there's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.20,0:30:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.59,0:30:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to go in and treat it, you know, because if you don't, the child will have
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.14,0:30:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin to fail and begin to see himself as failing or see himself as bad, and it's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.29,0:30:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.29,0:30:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Neurologic disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.40,0:30:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with balance of brain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.85,0:30:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.50,0:30:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.81,0:30:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if what I said is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.20,0:30:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The child has an insufficiency of prefrontal cortex suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.88,0:30:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.85,0:30:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.35,0:31:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.31,0:31:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would treat it, say, because the consequences of not treating it behaviorally, psychologically,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.38,0:31:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,emotionally are worse than the illness, say, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.99,0:31:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time you wear the dunce cap every day, you begin to feel like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.36,0:31:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's just because you can't control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.15,0:31:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.64,0:31:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I once had to wear the naughty mittens in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.20,0:31:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The naughty mittens?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.29,0:31:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naughty mittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.38,0:31:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to put like a dunce cap on, and they were naughty mittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.24,0:31:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you had to sit in the front row in kindergarten with the naughty mittens on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.64,0:31:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was from talking in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.64,0:31:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.31,0:31:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.75,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.27,0:31:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd mentioned at one of the lectures that when driving from Phoenix to Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.94,0:31:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you disappeared time by surrendering to the experiencing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.57,0:31:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.83,0:31:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.90,0:31:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting go of the resisting of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.90,0:32:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to please ask if you could just expand on that a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.96,0:32:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.99,0:32:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.26,0:32:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that you're running constantly a sense of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.98,0:32:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can either.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.02,0:32:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.02,0:32:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One is to not go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.14,0:32:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And just swamp yourself with a sense of time until time becomes itself oppressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.09,0:32:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can turn it around in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of resisting experiencing time, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.96,0:32:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you let go of resisting time, eventually you'll disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.73,0:32:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're experiencing time because you're trying to go faster than the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.73,0:32:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're feeling the time is like a delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.43,0:32:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like boring to drive all the way home from Phoenix, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.73,0:32:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:32:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.76,0:33:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it a drag on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.67,0:33:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a drag on your sense of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.78,0:33:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you let go in to change that, you can actually eventually eliminate the sense of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.96,0:33:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can leave Phoenix and two seconds later be impressed on experientially.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.66,0:33:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a certain thought, way of thinking that you only experience that which you resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you totally stop resisting, no experiencing occurs because there's nothing to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.07,0:33:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the general rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.16,0:33:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So if.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.91,0:33:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was trying to experience time, all right, so what I try to do is I try to just start experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.29,0:33:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.11,0:33:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, how do you experience time?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.64,0:33:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, you know, do you look at your watch and watch the clock, you know, tick or start thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.68,0:33:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is a subjective clock, a subjective experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.77,0:33:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How long ago you and I have been sitting here talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.00,0:34:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.66,0:34:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.11,0:34:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A minute or two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.03,0:34:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you were tracking it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.53,0:34:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I just got through telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.11,0:34:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tracking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.44,0:34:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you know it's one or two minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.94,0:34:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tracking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you knew it wasn't five hours, three days, a month and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.82,0:34:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.44,0:34:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were tracking it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.50,0:34:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.90,0:34:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.51,0:34:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.76,0:34:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do I stop resisting that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.36,0:34:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know you're resisting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.71,0:34:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.46,0:34:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty confused about the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.32,0:34:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's what I don't get, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.42,0:34:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not the fastest track for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.59,0:34:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.57,0:34:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that'd be two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.76,0:34:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go experiencing time itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.17,0:34:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can let go resisting the experiencing of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.38,0:34:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way will undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.92,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.90,0:35:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.61,0:35:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mind is tracking time all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.71,0:35:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.21,0:35:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how long we've been sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.51,0:35:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Approximately, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.03,0:35:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been tracking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.90,0:35:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.78,0:35:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.00,0:35:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is such a trickster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.69,0:35:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.98,0:35:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.65,0:35:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.07,0:35:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm interested in understanding more about spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.17,0:35:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.25,0:35:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the process of trying to accumulate it through receiving communion
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.92,0:35:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or listening to high-calibrated music, or?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.26,0:35:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't accumulate the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.03,0:35:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You intensify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.59,0:35:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to write on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:36:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.17,0:36:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can intensify it by devotion to beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.03,0:36:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and music, and spirituality, and prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.88,0:36:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.46,0:36:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a direct path to God, or a diversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.34,0:36:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, two things are going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.03,0:36:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One is you're increasing the spiritual energy itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.65,0:36:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is you're getting closer to...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.25,0:36:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of this surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was getting another...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.48,0:36:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can increase the spiritual energy by devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.51,0:36:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And all spiritual techniques and methods, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.59,0:36:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,tend to...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.05,0:36:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To increase the flow of the kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.67,0:36:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.00,0:36:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if that process was a direct path or a diversion,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.44,0:36:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like you talk about the astral circus,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.59,0:37:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the process of going to relics or listening to music
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.32,0:37:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or receiving communion, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.59,0:37:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, those are not diversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.05,0:37:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.82,0:37:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the astral circus is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.82,0:37:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all that ooh-la-la voices from other out-of-body teachers and crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.82,0:37:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.92,0:37:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.96,0:37:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's like in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.00,0:37:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're reading the tarot cards and getting readings and visiting psychics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.67,0:37:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.23,0:37:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if the psychic is correct, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.71,0:37:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one well-known one who is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.38,0:37:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary's at 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.13,0:37:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.15,0:37:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What he said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.73,0:37:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the question is, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.44,0:37:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.34,0:37:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.78,0:38:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, how do you relate to...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.01,0:38:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and treat the ego when it becomes afraid for its own annihilation?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.26,0:38:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.38,0:38:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you treat the ego when it becomes afraid of its own annihilation?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.34,0:38:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to say, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.51,0:38:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you would have to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.90,0:38:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it by surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.82,0:38:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Each positionality has a quasi-reality to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.13,0:38:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have to be willing to surrender that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.86,0:38:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I so-and-so, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.00,0:38:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you keep letting go until there's nothing left to let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.65,0:38:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What you'll come to is the bottom of the stack,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.80,0:38:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bottom of the stack is always, and then I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.86,0:39:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stop eating, then I'll starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.86,0:39:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I starve, I'll get thin, and I'll get a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.82,0:39:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll fall over, and then I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.96,0:39:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do, you always end up at the stack, and then I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.30,0:39:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,People won't like me. Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.78,0:39:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be expelled by society.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.07,0:39:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.13,0:39:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd use, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.59,0:39:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And each, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.13,0:39:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.73,0:39:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the stack is always death,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll die is what the ego's really afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.59,0:39:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because it identifies with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.96,0:39:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you say, all right, so let's die and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.13,0:39:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk into action. Let's hear it, big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.30,0:39:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the ego's bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.05,0:39:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the ego's bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.09,0:39:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever his worst threat is, you surrender to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.32,0:39:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be ugly, yes, and then the girls will go out with you, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.23,0:39:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you'll die of loneliness, yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.76,0:40:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So die already.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.92,0:40:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive and kicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.69,0:40:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is its fear of enlightenment different from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.19,0:40:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't such a thing as fear of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.17,0:40:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.30,0:40:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you're afraid of being in a state of infinite love and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.53,0:40:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really be afraid of that unless you're going to lose your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.96,0:40:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be under view anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.25,0:40:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.09,0:40:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.48,0:41:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So how are you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Immensely grateful to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.51,0:41:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.90,0:41:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.30,0:41:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to say thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.98,0:41:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.53,0:41:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All is known or unknowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.19,0:41:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.23,0:41:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You come along pretty good yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.11,0:41:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.34,0:41:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.63,0:41:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have any question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.53,0:42:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Life itself is so precious because I want your blessing for my spiritual journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.76,0:42:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.86,0:42:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.17,0:42:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For my spiritual journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.15,0:42:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants a blessing for his future journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.57,0:42:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Future journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.59,0:42:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.03,0:42:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean a future journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.61,0:42:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.40,0:42:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.01,0:42:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.48,0:42:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.23,0:42:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he said future journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.67,0:42:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.59,0:42:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.90,0:42:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, because you are here and you and I are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.30,0:42:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And obviously the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.76,0:42:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is because of your own spiritual integrity and desire to progress and reach
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.67,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.67,0:42:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.46,0:42:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.46,0:42:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We said it was one in 90 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.46,0:42:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One in 80 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.63,0:42:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.63,0:42:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty or 90 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.65,0:42:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep saying 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.65,0:42:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.65,0:42:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.55,0:42:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.55,0:42:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.55,0:42:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a right to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.55,0:42:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, it's either 80 or 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.55,0:42:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.55,0:42:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Start counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.55,0:42:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.55,0:42:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.55,0:42:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.55,0:42:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.55,0:42:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.94,0:42:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.94,0:42:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.03,0:43:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.21,0:43:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One in 80 or 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.78,0:43:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely desire to reach enlightenment is already an extreme rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.26,0:43:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just don't want all the emails telling us that you said 90 is an 80 or 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We tell them he's getting old now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.50,0:43:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know 80 from 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.13,0:43:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.78,0:43:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.78,0:43:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a difference between awareness and spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.40,0:43:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a difference between subjectivity?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.40,0:43:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A difference between awareness and subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.90,0:43:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a difference between the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.90,0:43:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.90,0:43:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One is content and the other is field.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.48,0:43:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is more diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.44,0:44:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Subjectivity you're talking about the sense of me and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.80,0:44:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is an aspect of consciousness itself that does not necessarily even involve an
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.82,0:44:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I or subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.82,0:44:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sense of personhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.11,0:44:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is aware without necessarily a person being aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.96,0:44:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can move beyond the witness to conscious awareness and the realization there is no
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.55,0:44:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,person, no one, no entity that is being aware or conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.48,0:44:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's consciousness becoming aware of its own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.71,0:44:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So the next step is to depersonalize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.48,0:44:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing is witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.03,0:44:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing is happening as a phenomenon all of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.32,0:45:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to interject the idea that there's an I that is doing the witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.63,0:45:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a narcissistic projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.53,0:45:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing is witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.53,0:45:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.61,0:45:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So the subjectivity is a presumption that there's an I that is doing this or to whom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.15,0:45:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.15,0:45:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any I?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.61,0:45:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.61,0:45:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a habit of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.51,0:45:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a habit of thought that there's an I that is conscious or aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.51,0:45:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no I that is conscious or aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.21,0:45:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say that the subjectivity is the essence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.50,0:45:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, subjectivity is the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.13,0:45:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an out there-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.86,0:45:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an in here-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.86,0:46:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm still stuck in I, the I in your prologue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.11,0:46:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a sentence that says, I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.13,0:46:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Subjectivity is the illumination of the self as the infinite I.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.63,0:46:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my other question is, what is the infinite I as opposed to self?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.26,0:46:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no opposition, but I don't understand the difference between self and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.69,0:46:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.69,0:46:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because I is subject or context, I-ness as a person, as a personhood, is a presumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.73,0:46:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.78,0:46:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a presumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.78,0:46:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.96,0:46:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let go of the presumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.51,0:47:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness can be aware without there being a person who's doing the aware-ness-ing, who's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.76,0:47:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,doing the being aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.63,0:47:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These are phenomena that occur of their own autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.48,0:47:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the point to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.86,0:47:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're occurring autonomously, not as subject-verb, not as subject-verb-object.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.25,0:47:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.09,0:47:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing is happening as a consequence of the fact that it is, that is its quality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.36,0:47:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.59,0:47:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's presumptive error to interject that there's an I to whom this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.86,0:47:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.86,0:47:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal I to whom this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.03,0:47:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is aware because that's the quality of awareness, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.26,0:47:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is awareness manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.26,0:47:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.26,0:47:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.55,0:47:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.55,0:47:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is awareness manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.55,0:47:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is awareness manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.73,0:47:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is awareness manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.73,0:47:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is awareness manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.73,0:48:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, manifest is the wrong word.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.11,0:48:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is awareness then?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.11,0:48:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How would the question arise without awareness of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.36,0:48:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the context of the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.23,0:48:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How could there be a cloud without a sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.59,0:48:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words instead of focusing on the cloud, you would focus on the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.80,0:48:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as things come by, that is the awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.63,0:48:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness of the content but what she's stuck in is...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.01,0:48:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.01,0:48:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the presumption that there's a you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.38,0:48:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that is doing the witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.44,0:48:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've interjected a subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.75,0:48:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of an imaginary pronoun called I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.50,0:48:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the infinite I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.80,0:49:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the infinite I?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite I is one that is beyond all pronouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.65,0:49:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quality of existence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.13,0:49:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.09,0:49:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You get those by meditation rather than logic or reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.67,0:49:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to nail it down, the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.23,0:49:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's more an awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.09,0:49:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to put it in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.61,0:49:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is all really beyond words.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.98,0:49:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an awareness that is a spontaneous emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.59,0:49:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look at it through meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.67,0:49:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than through the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.32,0:49:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking me the question through her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.46,0:49:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.76,0:49:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.92,0:50:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's arrived at through meditation, I would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.69,0:50:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,An understanding of it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.65,0:50:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, I know some people here in Sedona
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.28,0:50:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who have used a type of psychotherapy
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.48,0:50:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to help them process non-integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.50,0:50:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.53,0:50:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.42,0:50:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.13,0:50:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In Sedona, they're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.26,0:50:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people in Sedona are using psychotherapy
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.82,0:50:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to process...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.44,0:50:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotional negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.38,0:50:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotional negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.80,0:50:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychotherapy to process emotional negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.44,0:50:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.07,0:50:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know some people who have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.57,0:50:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You also speak of your own psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.13,0:50:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.96,0:50:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.96,0:51:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to speak about the role of psychotherapy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.09,0:51:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or psychoanalysis in the life of a spiritual seeker.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.98,0:51:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When is it appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.23,0:51:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When is it useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.40,0:51:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the life of a spiritual teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.28,0:51:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeker.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.00,0:51:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeker.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.67,0:51:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Student.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.42,0:51:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.76,0:51:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to know thyself, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.92,0:51:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the basic dictum?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.78,0:51:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Know thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.40,0:51:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So first know thyself before you go beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.78,0:51:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't even know what yourself is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.71,0:51:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that you want to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.05,0:51:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So psychotherapy, you know, analytic type therapy,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.71,0:51:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think is extremely helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.34,0:51:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand how the mind works.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.17,0:51:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mechanisms, how it originated
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.05,0:51:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in your own particular case.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.36,0:51:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So know thyself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.21,0:51:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose dictum is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.25,0:51:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.86,0:51:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Know thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.63,0:51:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.53,0:51:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.88,0:51:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.09,0:51:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.46,0:51:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Know thyself?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.26,0:51:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Know thyself is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.82,0:52:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.82,0:52:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.25,0:52:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Descartes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.75,0:52:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Before Descartes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.88,0:52:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, know thyself is written in some great statue
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.17,0:52:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or something, one of the first premises
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.40,0:52:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of ancient Greek philosophy or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.80,0:52:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, know thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.80,0:52:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Know thyself, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.51,0:52:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you recommend using traditional psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.51,0:52:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or a more multidisciplinary spiritually oriented practitioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.40,0:52:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.96,0:52:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too general a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.23,0:52:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what a multi or, you know, what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.76,0:52:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like someone who is aware of your work, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.17,0:52:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.01,0:52:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And has that, and is using that as part
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.51,0:52:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of their understanding of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.21,0:52:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.57,0:52:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Versus someone who is Freudian, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.71,0:52:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.03,0:52:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Either.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.26,0:52:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.26,0:52:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.57,0:52:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that the analyst is an atheist doesn't affect you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.90,0:52:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's not concerned with that, nor is he even going
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.19,0:52:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring it in, you know, except as anecdotally, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.07,0:53:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But any analyst, Jungian, Freudian, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.36,0:53:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to know thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.96,0:53:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.73,0:53:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first dictum of something or other that's famous
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.51,0:53:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't remember what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.82,0:53:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still trying to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.42,0:53:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come to me in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.23,0:53:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come to me in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.36,0:53:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.80,0:53:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.07,0:53:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, I just wanted to ask you if you could touch on if one really wants
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.38,0:54:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to devote, you know, intensely to their life, you know, to just giving up,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.42,0:54:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering the self completely, if that should come
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.55,0:54:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,about on a spiritual aspirant's journey at some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.55,0:54:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the necessary requisites you would say as a teacher to a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.42,0:54:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And also any possible, like, pitfalls or things that one should watch out for,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.09,0:54:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps, on such an endeavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.17,0:54:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What endeavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.92,0:54:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What endeavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.46,0:54:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.86,0:54:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.28,0:54:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.48,0:54:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.88,0:54:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To surrender everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.94,0:54:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the pitfalls?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.82,0:54:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any pitfalls?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.46,0:54:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, just die or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.13,0:54:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.09,0:54:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I mean, I know you've touched on a lot of your books on the requisites, but, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.28,0:54:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be the requisite a student would, no, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.82,0:54:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.50,0:54:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the bottom line.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.53,0:54:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.69,0:54:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You could add the bottom line no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.78,0:54:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That would make any technique even more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.21,0:54:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.26,0:55:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you want, you're picking surrendering, wanting this, and eventually you reach, oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.11,0:55:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wanting to reach the state of not wanting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.32,0:55:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I let go of that wanting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.09,0:55:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.90,0:55:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.84,0:55:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're, like, untethering the balloon and where it might go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.73,0:55:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go in the following direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.46,0:55:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.55,0:55:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.61,0:55:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.07,0:55:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to let go of wanting this, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.50,0:55:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you let go wanting to?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.03,0:55:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of all wanting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.96,0:55:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.21,0:55:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, Susan, I'm first time here, and I've been four year and a half still studying you,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.86,0:55:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's been a great journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.98,0:55:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is not about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.86,0:55:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to speak slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.55,0:55:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is about studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.88,0:55:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.94,0:56:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.05,0:56:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.13,0:56:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.19,0:56:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.36,0:56:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.44,0:56:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.48,0:56:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.26,0:56:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.30,0:56:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.32,0:56:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.44,0:56:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.57,0:56:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're someone who is suffering from ALS, and they deny, actually, that that's the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.07,0:56:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,illness they got, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.96,0:56:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They have ALS, and they're denying that they have ALS?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.53,0:56:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.88,0:56:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.55,0:56:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you recommend some spiritual tool which could be maybe helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.84,0:56:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to convince them that they have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.30,0:56:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really to convince them, but I just stated that how they, I don't know, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.86,0:56:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,perceive it but is there any spiritual tool that they it could help them for
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.26,0:56:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the illness itself except the diagnosis yeah yeah well not specifically about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.19,0:56:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing the details of the situation there may be reasons for it I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.32,0:57:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,try to change his mind why do you want change his mind I just thought that it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.90,0:57:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,would be good to accept something what it is because you think that he should
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.01,0:57:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,accept it why should he accept it that's a good
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.98,0:57:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,question like a good idea to you that's because you don't have ALS you think
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.05,0:57:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's great he should accept it and his own psychology will take care of it in
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.69,0:57:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,due time and you know the denial can be a protective mechanism that's normal
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.90,0:57:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if he accepts it are they going to cure it no so he's not holding off a cure yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.01,0:57:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and probably maybe part of the denial is an aspect of the ALS itself you see so it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.84,0:57:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,could be a self-protective mechanism and I would frankly not mess with it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.80,0:58:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,myself good question procedural question what is calibration level of Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.92,0:58:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandments what calibrated level of energy of Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.26,0:58:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandments
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.88,0:58:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the calibration of the Ten Commandments think a thousand I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,mess with them I see people mess with them on television I'm put I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.53,0:58:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it calibrates at ten blasphemy calibrates at ten and I watch people
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.78,0:59:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,encouraging doing black blasphemy and encouraging others to do it which
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.88,0:59:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at ten and that is the one for which there is no forgiveness to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.80,0:59:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the one for which there is no forgiveness to encourage others to do
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.32,0:59:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that that you encourage to do it you self encourage others to do
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.38,0:59:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that which for which there is no forgiveness to me is the height of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.71,0:59:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,wickedness yeah the height of wickedness it's such a great privilege to be here I
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.82,0:59:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just want to thank you for your exquisite communication both you're
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.63,1:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching in what you communicate in silence thank you like you I'd just like
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.42,1:00:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,honor to be here with you and everyone here. My question is, how do you differentiate the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.05,1:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,difference between spiritual joy and the payoff of the ego or the juice that it gets?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.73,1:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Between joy and what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.88,1:00:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Payoff of the ego and the juice it gets.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.65,1:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego getting, oh, he's talking about legitimate joy. Well, they have a different quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.82,1:00:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really confuse joy with ego satisfaction. You win the lottery, you know, you feel ego
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.63,1:01:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfaction. Joy is something that happens without any particular occasion to bring it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.15,1:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on, necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.13,1:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.26,1:01:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy stems from within. Something out there precipitates it, but the joy comes from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.82,1:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear a piece of beautiful music and you begin to cry with joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.46,1:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.42,1:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The music precipitates it, but the joy is coming from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.80,1:01:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, Susan, I'd like to thank you for your love for your husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.01,1:01:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It is inspiring and very uplifting.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.01,1:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has been asked in the previous years several times, and I want to just give a little
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.15,1:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,preamble.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.53,1:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in college and I had to take a math, complicated math course, and I was a beginner at
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.84,1:02:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,math, the professor really didn't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.26,1:02:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He really didn't have a concept of not knowing what he knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.71,1:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not knowing what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.63,1:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What he knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.07,1:02:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What he knew. What the professor knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.65,1:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He assumed that his students knew what he was talking about. For example, in calculus.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.90,1:02:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. The professor assumed that the student was getting what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.07,1:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.44,1:02:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.59,1:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So he didn't have a step-down transformer to make it simple and palatable.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.07,1:02:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.11,1:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My question to you is, and so I'm hoping you can make it simple and palatable.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.38,1:02:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.84,1:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculus. Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.61,1:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.01,1:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.11,1:02:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The differential calculus. I'll try that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.05,1:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.38,1:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that self-esteem is a very important stepping stone to the growth of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.42,1:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If self-esteem is damaged and the person doesn't yet have an experience of self-esteem,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.15,1:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't have an experience of self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.59,1:03:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have an experience of self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.61,1:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have an experience of self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.65,1:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The essential knowledge of God, of what you are, is that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.17,1:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one really go about repairing that wound?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.59,1:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you set up for yourself your own spiritual curriculum, and then you live up to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.96,1:03:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that, you get a sense of self-esteem because you know that you are...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.03,1:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aligned with your goals, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.96,1:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by curriculum?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.09,1:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like you go to a Bible study group, or you would go to a religious...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.32,1:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. So basically...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.05,1:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A regime that you live by.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.07,1:04:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, you kind of can one, say, a religious or gathering a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.71,1:04:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying then is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.71,1:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that a person really who is atheist...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.09,1:04:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.84,1:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.13,1:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.61,1:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.15,1:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.19,1:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Has no hope while they're that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.50,1:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.13,1:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The atheist can feel quite secure because, first of all, he doesn't have God to contend with.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.03,1:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.48,1:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is a snap.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.48,1:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So ignorance is a bliss sometimes, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.67,1:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But then he begins to wonder later on in life as he gets more mature.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.46,1:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.76,1:04:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if this is the...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.59,1:04:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.61,1:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.09,1:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gets more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.28,1:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He moves from atheist to agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.13,1:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great improvement.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.17,1:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.71,1:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheist is...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.76,1:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so smart I can prove that God doesn't exist, which means you're an idiot to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.88,1:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's ever disproven the existence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.51,1:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.71,1:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You become an agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.98,1:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then as an agnostic, you can check out the validity of various pathways.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.67,1:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I suggest for the agnostic...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.48,1:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Agnostic or the unbeliever, Buddhism.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.48,1:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha, you don't have to believe anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.42,1:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.51,1:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to believe in divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.86,1:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.42,1:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to, you know, Zen Institute and you learn meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.40,1:05:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You just meditate, period.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.07,1:05:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just meditate the way they tell you to meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.71,1:05:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever comes up, comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.05,1:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.00,1:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's very, very useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.26,1:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.82,1:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And very genuine because it's your own...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.76,1:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence of...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.03,1:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.46,1:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So all they do is teach you a meditative technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.42,1:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always tell atheists, first become an agnostic and then go for a Zen meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.42,1:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So then to deal with one ego, with one's ego, a healthy self-esteem has to be in place.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.05,1:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.57,1:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.69,1:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.44,1:06:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.09,1:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To make self-esteem easier to get, set your standards, you know, low so they're easy to reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.90,1:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at the length on that baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.57,1:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's huge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.73,1:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, look out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.28,1:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.63,1:06:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.01,1:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless our children.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.84,1:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.07,1:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are these children?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.92,1:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them is home.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.13,1:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one is attending the seminar with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.51,1:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless your children, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.13,1:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.21,1:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.38,1:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.92,1:07:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.30,1:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shake it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.84,1:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath and exhale.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.88,1:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then click.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.57,1:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.67,1:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like looking in the mirror and there's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.61,1:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little scary the first time it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.76,1:07:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge lens on that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.67,1:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You look in the mirror and you don't see anything looking back at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.69,1:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's time to call the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.55,1:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a side effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.21,1:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.46,1:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.98,1:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is that there's a concern that the calibration of the world has fallen from 207 to 204.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.15,1:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.86,1:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really feel personally responsible.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.73,1:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.40,1:07:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.44,1:07:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you for...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.40,1:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.59,1:07:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered who did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.65,1:08:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Confession is good for the soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.30,1:08:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.11,1:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.07,1:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So the question is possibly is there a benefit for spiritual students such as us on the path that we,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.03,1:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as beacons of light that we've gotten from you,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.85,1:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,go out into the world and live in certain communities and help counterbalance negativities in that communities?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.72,1:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of doubt there's a physicality to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.88,1:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.57,1:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.03,1:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.23,1:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a regional effect, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.10,1:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is a regional effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.28,1:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think TM proved that many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.32,1:08:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.36,1:08:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That if over 5% of the population are meditating,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.82,1:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the crime rate drops by 90% or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.57,1:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know when I first moved to Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.47,1:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the number of spiritual people
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.11,1:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,was more than 5% of the population.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.85,1:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the first class we had on A Course in Miracles?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.88,1:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There was over 100 there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.93,1:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at that time, there was only 3,000 in the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.18,1:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So they all began meditating.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.10,1:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were already over 5% of the town's population.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.43,1:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And according to TM's research,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.77,1:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if over 5% of the population meditates,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.11,1:09:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the crime rate drops and everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.03,1:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And in those years, crime was unknown.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.07,1:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever locked their cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.30,1:09:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing was ever stolen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.47,1:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no such thing as a burglary.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.73,1:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could be, yes, that it does have a regional effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.02,1:09:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a surprise to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.14,1:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It does indeed have a regional effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.57,1:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.53,1:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say the 12 disciples,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.47,1:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the scatter to the winds?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.50,1:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.31,1:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.68,1:09:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.39,1:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an expression of Christ's instructions to the apostles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.15,1:09:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.85,1:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.40,1:10:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we were to start little spiritual communities
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.06,1:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the country or even the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.51,1:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have an effect, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.40,1:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That would have an effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.27,1:10:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.06,1:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would possibly keep the calibration from falling?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.36,1:10:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that causality?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.52,1:10:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.67,1:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it isn't that it would raise it over the whole world,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.39,1:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it would raise it of that community, I would think, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.14,1:10:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.05,1:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, a certain number of people calibrating high
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.25,1:10:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is already affecting the collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.97,1:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we say, what's the consciousness level of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.85,1:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we're calibrating the collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.32,1:10:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.43,1:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.18,1:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, but there apparently is a regional effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.57,1:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.02,1:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's certain areas of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.96,1:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When we did, calibrated the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.39,1:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of various areas of the world in various countries,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.51,1:10:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there were some countries in which the calibrated level
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.97,1:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness was below that of criminality.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.02,1:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.35,1:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in this hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.61,1:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one very obvious one, calibrates at 70.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.19,1:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very low.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.43,1:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.46,1:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.14,1:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.68,1:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.92,1:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an interesting question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.96,1:11:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.21,1:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.81,1:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.06,1:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you would have like a contagion effect, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.85,1:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The more spiritual people are involved in spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.94,1:11:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in other words, a certain contagion of spiritual interests.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.07,1:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.14,1:11:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.56,1:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.56,1:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.15,1:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.15,1:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.15,1:11:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.15,1:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So they have a contagious effect on people in the community when.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.34,1:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.72,1:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.72,1:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If a number of spiritual people move into town, it has like a contagious effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.85,1:11:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like if somebody goes to church, they say, you want to go to church with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.05,1:11:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like, next thing you know, they're going to church, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.14,1:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.50,1:12:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.96,1:12:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you once again for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.56,1:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And all that you give to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.06,1:12:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving down to Sedona from Toronto recently, I encountered some automobile trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.22,1:12:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some automobile's trouble?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.42,1:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.71,1:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.71,1:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, she .
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.71,1:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she had trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.71,1:12:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.71,1:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I, at one point, I heard a voice, just a soft voice through the thinking that said, check
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.71,1:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.06,1:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.06,1:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.06,1:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.06,1:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.06,1:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.06,1:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.06,1:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.06,1:12:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.06,1:12:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.06,1:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pulled over into a gas station.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.06,1:12:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And immediately someone came to my aid who knew exactly what it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.06,1:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And helped me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.06,1:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave me wonderful advice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.06,1:13:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then consequently, arriving in Sedona, another one filled the place and took over
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.31,1:13:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with regards to the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.31,1:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What ...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.51,1:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What ...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.53,1:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What it sometimes seems to be is that there are more angels amongst us
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.60,1:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,than we might always recognize.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.23,1:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't call them that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.22,1:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.72,1:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it dawns on us later.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.43,1:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.43,1:13:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The statistical likelihood of that happening was about zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.31,1:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be some type of, I don't know what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.06,1:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a transference or something that occurs in the eyes, within the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.77,1:13:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, are the eyes the window of the soul?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.27,1:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be just a profound nonverbal communication that occurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.23,1:13:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, almost telepathic, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.00,1:14:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very, yes, very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.64,1:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, almost telepathic, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.13,1:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.89,1:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathic, we have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.94,1:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.10,1:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathic calibrates over 250, 255.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.05,1:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathic communication and all of those calibrated about 250.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.09,1:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.69,1:14:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.68,1:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are periods in your spiritual work where all these phenomena come and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.84,1:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a period where you're very telepathic.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.84,1:14:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's almost a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.80,1:14:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what people think in the instant they walk up towards you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.85,1:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You already got what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.46,1:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just pick up the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.53,1:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you went through that for a couple of years one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.82,1:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost a nuisance, like, you know, what everybody was thinking all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.47,1:15:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.06,1:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.06,1:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.56,1:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through a time of great fear, despair, agony, and confusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.78,1:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt very shaken up by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.28,1:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still feel paralyzed and still trying to recover.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.94,1:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something precipitate it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.38,1:15:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you ascribe it to?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.67,1:15:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.21,1:15:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.32,1:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably have lots of negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.18,1:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.84,1:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.18,1:15:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, I'm just dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.94,1:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You use all the spiritual tools you have at your command and pray for God's help.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.81,1:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you come out on the other side of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.80,1:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.53,1:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds simple enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.18,1:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.18,1:16:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As my spiritual teacher, could you just tell me it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.34,1:16:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As a spiritual teacher telling you what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.64,1:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.73,1:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.84,1:16:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.81,1:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Life's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.23,1:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.60,1:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.80,1:16:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing's happening, you're probably not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.80,1:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.43,1:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling content and happy all the time because it's a bad sign because you're not getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.63,1:16:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.56,1:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.52,1:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the reason people go through things like that is they're pulling up a stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.47,1:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stack about something.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.72,1:16:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to the bottom, work through all that stack, then that stack is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.57,1:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be quiet for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.03,1:16:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you maybe start on another.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.23,1:16:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.36,1:16:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.85,1:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.60,1:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.75,1:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.90,1:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I never met you before.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.60,1:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.90,1:17:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm a little nervous to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.67,1:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not nervous enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.64,1:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So it came up with calibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.22,1:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just started some Sufi dancing and singing, and I'm really connecting with God that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.72,1:17:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw Allah, infinity, calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.85,1:17:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you spoke...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.63,1:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke about the Quran, which was hard to hear what it said.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.98,1:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I think my question is, how do I trust myself on a spiritual path to find the things which fit my karma on my right way to go when I still have a lot of ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.64,1:17:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.39,1:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you just pray for God's will for you and follow the simple things.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.47,1:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe meditate half an hour in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.63,1:18:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe meditate half an hour at night or 15 minutes in the morning at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.61,1:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Read some spiritual scripture periodically and meditate on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.50,1:18:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you have a feeling in your heart or something which can guide you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.43,1:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to worry about all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.88,1:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.69,1:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask God for his direction for your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.64,1:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You pick a psalm that you think is very powerful for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.61,1:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I start the Christian miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.50,1:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.52,1:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.35,1:18:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to move from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.82,1:18:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.10,1:18:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're sort of lit.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.35,1:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've asked God help, God's help to reach God, then, you know, you get special help at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.69,1:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.56,1:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,God sends special help.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.63,1:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For your angels, angelic beings.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.05,1:18:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.21,1:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.46,1:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.14,1:19:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor and a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.72,1:19:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.35,1:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is on your first physical incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.92,1:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in general.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.60,1:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At birth, on your first physical incarnation, do you come in to the world at over 600?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.51,1:19:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose physical incarnation?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.27,1:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At any one.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.85,1:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.90,1:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.55,1:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.89,1:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't come into the world over 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.93,1:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I was wondering, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.77,1:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600, you wouldn't need to incarnate in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.14,1:19:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already transcended to a heavenly realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.89,1:19:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly realms are 600 and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.82,1:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, how do you have negative personal karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.21,1:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On your first physical incarnation at birth?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.75,1:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.14,1:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.44,1:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever hear of the serpent of the Garden of Eden?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.30,1:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.57,1:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The fallen man?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.69,1:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about as good a legend as you can find to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.10,1:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if everyone went through that, the seduction of Adam and Eve, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.47,1:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's the origin of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.90,1:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.31,1:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.77,1:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.93,1:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.50,1:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.77,1:20:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.81,1:20:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.84,1:20:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.85,1:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.88,1:20:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.89,1:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.92,1:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.96,1:20:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.97,1:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.02,1:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.06,1:20:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.07,1:20:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.02,1:20:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.80,1:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.92,1:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.97,1:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.18,1:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,disobedience for which an angry God threw mankind into this realm I see it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.68,1:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence of the child which is within everyone fell to the seduction of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.76,1:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the serpent of evil so it's like evil wanted to take over the realm of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.06,1:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,goodness and sent a messenger the the weakness of the pert the weakness of Eve
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.48,1:21:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,was not her personal weakness but the seduction of the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.40,1:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,within her for which she was not equipped like the guru falls I say the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.52,1:21:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,fault is the teacher of that teacher who did not forewarn of what may arise so my
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.47,1:21:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding of my acceptance of Genesis is limited I see it as the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.47,1:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,innocence of the child within her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.60,1:22:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of ignorance so even like Jesus Christ only had the one incarnation oh I don't
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.28,1:22:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,know and I couldn't tell you okay I'll ask him I know what you know traditional
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.42,1:22:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,religion says about it I don't actually know the answer what do you want me to do
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.97,1:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you want me to shake hands with people
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.88,1:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,okay I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.11,1:22:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll move along faster yes speak up well that works out that works out perfect I
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.50,1:22:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have a question ah haha I just super duper there's just nowhere I'd rather be
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.23,1:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just want to be here good to see you yeah yeah so then we shake the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.84,1:23:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,hands of this many people already yes I'm a teacher high school teacher right
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.23,1:23:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a high school teacher yes yes slowly and near the man Mike okay I'm a
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.19,1:23:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a high school teacher, yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.03,1:23:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering what now the purpose of K-12 education is.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.93,1:23:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What now the purpose of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.30,1:23:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If the universities are calibrating below 200, what now is the purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.81,1:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's my purpose as a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.11,1:23:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's not the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.64,1:23:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't the only people that are around.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.56,1:23:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we can live very well without Yale, Harvard, and Columbia
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.44,1:23:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and all those that calibrate 190 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.23,1:23:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sitting right here at 440.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.46,1:23:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is not now what I signed up for,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.85,1:23:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can see the seeds of what you talk about in my world.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.89,1:23:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look around to find that which is more integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.93,1:24:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and more in line with your own worldview and your own values.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.00,1:24:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as working for a company.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.64,1:24:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start with a company and then find that that company's values
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.23,1:24:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and their mode of sovereignty are not within your realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.68,1:24:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't mean you need to change your profession.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.61,1:24:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need to do is find the circumstance that is more in accordance
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.47,1:24:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with your own alignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.80,1:24:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you religious at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.88,1:24:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Very.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.64,1:24:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.02,1:24:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of religion, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.69,1:24:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what I would call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.77,1:24:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read all of your books, and I would consider you my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.60,1:24:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.43,1:24:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.14,1:24:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're talking about is spirituality, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.60,1:24:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.92,1:24:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what you want is an institution that is sincerely dedicated,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.47,1:24:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to developing the student's mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.38,1:24:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the integrity of the student's mind, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.10,1:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.72,1:24:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that can happen in public school?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.31,1:25:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on the public school, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.81,1:25:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.26,1:25:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there could be some school somewhere
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.50,1:25:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is still maintained as the primary goal,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.43,1:25:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or you may have to go to the private school system
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.38,1:25:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or the parochial, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.34,1:25:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.59,1:25:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's, you know, dedicated to the integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.21,1:25:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of the student and not to some political program?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.52,1:25:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the difficulty in today's world.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.36,1:25:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, No Child Left Behind has affected all public schools
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.10,1:25:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because of, it's politicized it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.47,1:25:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.39,1:25:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.92,1:25:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.72,1:25:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what No Child Left Behind means.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.23,1:25:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It means everybody gets promoted no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.65,1:25:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a little bit different from that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.84,1:25:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everyone, everyone must have the same education.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.84,1:25:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.14,1:25:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It, there, you don't really,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.31,1:25:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,need a teacher because the curriculum is being standardized. I see. Everybody has
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.13,1:26:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the matches standardized, yes. I don't know what to say about it. I'd have to
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.03,1:26:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you a bit more about it. It's a challenge. I don't know. I went to State
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.77,1:26:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teachers College for two years and they were supposed to understand the
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.43,1:26:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,curriculum and you were supposed to bring forth their intellectual
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.50,1:26:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,capacities to the fullest. So what you accomplish with one student might be
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.53,1:26:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,sufficient, considering what their IQ is, but this student over here, they expect
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.98,1:26:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're going to accomplish a good deal more with and give them extra work,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.09,1:26:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,etc. Right, right. That's what we're doing. That's what we're told to do. That's very good. And to support those who cannot do the work. I think education is a great thing to get involved in. Thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.68,1:26:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Two best years of my college life. State Teachers College. Eighty bucks
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.84,1:27:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a year tuition and free books. Boy, I'll tell you. I went to the same Teachers College my father went to for two years. Hello, Dr. Hawkins. Yes. I really appreciate you having a lecture on my birthday. It's been the greatest gift that I could ever have. I tried to accommodate you, you know. All I could ever ask for. I don't have a question this time. Oh, okay. I want to say thank you, but it seems.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.03,1:27:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The gratitude is. Very nice. How old are you today? I'm 47 today. Oh, very good. Very good. Which means I'm 11. I get to be 11 again because I add the numbers together. Oh, oh. So I'm 11 all over again. So I'm just very grateful to be here. Yes. To both of you very much. And I love you both very much. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.03,1:27:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The age of ancient Greece. Few people lived to be 47 in ancient Rome. Let me go. What was the average age of death in ancient Rome? I think 28 or 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.56,1:27:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not 28.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.80,1:28:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too high. Hi. Yes. My lesson for the day in Course in Miracles is there is a peace that Christ bestows on us. There is a peace that what? Christ bestows on us. Oh, yes. Yes. I thought maybe you could just say something about that. No, I think it's self-descriptive. Those who accept that Christ is one Savior, that Christ is a great avatar.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.64,1:29:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That Christ will be your advocate before the Father. Those who believe in my name, I will speak for them before the Father. That is a terrific comfort to have that, to know that. Is it not? Yes. Yes. And in itself, it's just a blessing, you know. Yes. I'd like to go down on bended knee. What did he say? You'll find out. Oh, I know what you say. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.27,1:30:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I love you. I love you and I love your love. Yes. I'm honored to be with you, be here with you. My question is, what to you is true intimacy in relationships? What is true intimacy? I think sharing, you know, the most intimate thing is the sharing of one's inner spiritual, inner thoughts and
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.10,1:30:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sensitivities and ways of seeing things. The physicality you can experience with anybody, see? And if you know the right neighborhood for $20, that doesn't take long. It takes, it takes, I watch TV the same as you. But I think to really share your inner most, most sensitive sensitivities and concerns and
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.85,1:30:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the things you're working through results in a profound intimacy in a spiritual manner, see? So I say relationships that are mature are parallel, side by side and parallel, because you're both aligned with the same destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.93,1:31:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Relationships that are, that hold you back are in horizontal, solar plexus to solar plexus. What can I get out of it? What can she get out of it? Who's going to win? Who's going to win this argument? You know, to share your
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.03,1:31:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,really inner sensitivities, the things you don't really want to tell anybody about,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.97,1:31:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is the development of a spiritual trust, because you know what the people at work would think of
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.10,1:31:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you if you reveal that such a thing. You know, I felt scared to death to go out and call down
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.42,1:31:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,this customer. But you could tell your wife that, you know, I'm scared to crapless about
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.68,1:31:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to the president of this big corporation, you know? And she says, honey, I believe in you,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.31,1:31:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're doing it for me and the kids,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.13,1:31:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and somehow you feel better and you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.02,1:31:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my God, I'll do it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.55,1:31:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that working back and forth with each other,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.82,1:31:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the most intimate thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.93,1:31:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is to share your passing inner doubts and thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.93,1:31:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you're working through right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.59,1:32:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.72,1:32:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that implies a great deal of trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.06,1:32:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because any one of those things that you confide
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.18,1:32:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,could then be used in a less integrous relationship
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.18,1:32:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack you with, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.97,1:32:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't even have confidence in yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.59,1:32:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, a clipper, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.73,1:32:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't trust people that are not trustable.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.97,1:32:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to first define that they're trustable,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.23,1:32:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they're not going to use it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.56,1:32:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as some kind of an attack against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.10,1:32:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So some people are sort of congenitally malevolent,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.46,1:32:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've got to watch out for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.84,1:32:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of vicious by nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.15,1:32:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to get pleasure out of wickedness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.36,1:32:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.26,1:32:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's a very good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.92,1:33:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.77,1:33:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.47,1:33:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.02,1:33:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I need to hear regarding
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.06,1:33:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of this consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.48,1:33:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.55,1:33:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. What do you need to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.60,1:33:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I need to hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.22,1:33:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she need to hear to elevate her consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.02,1:33:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she need to hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.46,1:33:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.68,1:33:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I have a better question.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.81,1:33:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were transcending,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.76,1:33:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were transcending the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.22,1:33:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that you would feel excruciating pain
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.22,1:33:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,until something was resolved.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.42,1:33:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys speak closer to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.68,1:33:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that as you were transcending
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.38,1:33:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.77,1:33:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you would feel excruciating pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.15,1:33:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What needed to be resolved,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.93,1:33:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or what was resolved as you were transcending those levels
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.52,1:34:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to resolve that pain in your body?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.31,1:34:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.73,1:34:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talking about physical pain or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.10,1:34:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.01,1:34:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when you were transcending different levels?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.93,1:34:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.22,1:34:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.43,1:34:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.81,1:34:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have physical ailments.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.68,1:34:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. All kinds of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.89,1:34:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.44,1:34:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.71,1:34:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.86,1:34:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.42,1:34:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was psychic,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.47,1:34:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but also it could cause enough stress
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.64,1:34:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to cause physical illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.19,1:34:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.77,1:34:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So what were the things that you resolved
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.31,1:34:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to alleviate that pain
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.97,1:34:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as you were transcending the levels?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.11,1:34:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the specifics.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.35,1:34:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too general.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.65,1:34:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to put, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.35,1:34:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because at different levels,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.50,1:34:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there's different things that come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.39,1:34:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one of us have different things
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.22,1:34:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that will come up at different levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.53,1:34:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a generalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.26,1:34:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on what you're working on, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.39,1:34:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you're working on jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.88,1:34:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be a different archetype
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.06,1:34:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in the collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.27,1:34:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to hit a different chakra
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.23,1:34:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in the chakra system.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.93,1:35:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So depending on what kind of conflict
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.31,1:35:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.89,1:35:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.60,1:35:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.31,1:35:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.73,1:35:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like possessiveness could be the solar plexus, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.93,1:35:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And heart, pain in the heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.38,1:35:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with love, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.11,1:35:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could be related.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.35,1:35:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's related to the chakra system.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.30,1:35:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.55,1:35:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in that B?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.01,1:35:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,B what?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.09,1:35:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That vitamin, you know, little B's
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.77,1:35:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,produce something that balances your acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.86,1:35:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've mentioned it two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.82,1:35:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Little B's?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.77,1:35:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,B's.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.60,1:35:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,B3?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.00,1:35:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.60,1:35:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,B, a B's.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.42,1:35:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.46,1:35:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.26,1:35:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.94,1:35:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.05,1:36:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.30,1:36:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Propolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.96,1:36:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Propolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.42,1:36:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,B propolis balances the acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.60,1:36:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,system and will help get you out of a negativity
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.72,1:36:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,quicker than anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.10,1:36:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.19,1:36:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you chew on some B propolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.35,1:36:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like magic, but it actually works.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.98,1:36:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.68,1:36:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came up here for the blessing in meeting...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.05,1:36:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.10,1:36:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.27,1:36:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.43,1:36:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She says it's a blessing in meeting us.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.73,1:36:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.27,1:36:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to sign that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.25,1:36:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.52,1:36:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, B propolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.68,1:36:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,B propolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.77,1:36:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,B propolis tends to balance the acupuncture system
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.60,1:36:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it back in balance after it's been blown out.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.78,1:36:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.76,1:36:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.96,1:36:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a real spiritual devotee,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.77,1:36:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it really keeps you busy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.21,1:37:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy sitting under a Bodhi tree, cross-legged,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.86,1:37:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,chewing on propolis, going, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.35,1:37:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,going like this and going, ah, at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.61,1:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.92,1:37:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's enough to keep you busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.00,1:37:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.27,1:37:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Honkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.27,1:37:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.52,1:37:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.93,1:37:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.72,1:37:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about when you wrote about the harmonic convergence in,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.26,1:37:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember October 86, and I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.56,1:37:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the museum once and it said when Christ was born,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.80,1:37:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he was, you know, of course that's, or the Buddha was born,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.42,1:37:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it would raise the consciousness of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.06,1:37:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it possible during the harmonic convergence
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.57,1:37:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that an avatar-type person could have been born
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.14,1:37:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and changed the consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.72,1:37:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and raised it that one month?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.50,1:37:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, because it stayed up there for years,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.27,1:38:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and only went, in fact, it continued up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.47,1:38:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It went up from 190 to 204 in late 87.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.64,1:38:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It subsequently went up to 207,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.72,1:38:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it went back down to 205,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.52,1:38:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and now to 204.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.69,1:38:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you ever ask the arm,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.10,1:38:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.44,1:38:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what did it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.73,1:38:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pope is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.26,1:38:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pope is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.47,1:38:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.60,1:38:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't keep track of what the Pope's telling people?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.92,1:38:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.31,1:38:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong religion, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.72,1:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Pope is quite integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.48,1:38:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.25,1:38:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that relativism plus Islam,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.75,1:38:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the combination of the two,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.61,1:39:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,one is Luciferic and the other is Satanic.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.39,1:39:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but what,
