Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.63,1:39:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.78,1:39:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was wondering.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.09,1:39:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the natural evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.75,1:39:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It reaches, you know, it's like saying
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.10,1:39:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,what made the sea rise to a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.52,1:39:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.22,1:39:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The total activity of the total sea over, you know, decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.93,1:39:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know that Jesus wasn't born or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.44,1:39:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we did the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.98,1:39:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,during the, showing its evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.68,1:39:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,over great decades, archaeological ages, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.89,1:39:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as we get to the more, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.06,1:39:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the more recent archaeological age,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.39,1:39:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we track its evolution through the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.77,1:39:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, in the book, I forget which book,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.06,1:39:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it tracks it according to archaeological age.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.56,1:39:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,During which archaeological age,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.57,1:39:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what was the consciousness level of life on the planet?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.52,1:39:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see that it,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.92,1:39:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so a quality of consciousness is that it tends to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.35,1:39:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
