Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.00,1:40:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.89,1:40:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I can never tell when they work.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.94,1:40:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.52,1:40:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.46,1:40:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we're not going to get to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.35,1:40:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll just run as fast as we can
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.35,1:40:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'm going to shake everybody's hand and we'll.
