Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.85,1:40:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.77,1:40:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.65,1:40:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just run like rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.93,1:40:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.60,1:40:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.25,1:40:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I do hands-on energy healing
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.35,1:40:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to ask you,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.51,1:40:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm working with a client,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.60,1:40:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the beliefs or the prayers
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.52,1:40:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that I should be focusing on
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.52,1:40:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and what should they be focusing on
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.01,1:40:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to heal themselves?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.51,1:41:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you think of the highest thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.60,1:41:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can think of.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.68,1:41:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gratitude for God's love,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.15,1:41:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your acceptance of God's love,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.40,1:41:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that the reality of the self
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.89,1:41:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,involves divine balance,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.40,1:41:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,divine healing,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.35,1:41:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have the patient accept
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.11,1:41:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,divine balance, divine harmony,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.59,1:41:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that my, let's say, autonomic nervous system,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.81,1:41:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my sympathetic nervous system,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.47,1:41:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,my acupuncture system, whatever it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.76,1:41:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,manifests divine harmony and balance.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.98,1:41:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The self with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.60,1:41:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,obviously intrinsically,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.90,1:41:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,has the quality of healingness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.32,1:41:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and divine balance.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.60,1:41:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmony and balance,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.75,1:41:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,subject to karmic limitations.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.75,1:42:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you ask for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.86,1:42:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for all within yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.32,1:42:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,now or forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.14,1:42:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that could be impeding it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.48,1:42:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.36,1:42:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to become aware of anything within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.67,1:42:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that could be impeding your healing,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.72,1:42:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, unconscious guilt or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.76,1:42:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.89,1:42:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-healing is spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.06,1:42:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.96,1:42:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.11,1:42:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It involves many modalities.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.06,1:42:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in exploring them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.68,1:42:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiropractic, acupuncture,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.02,1:42:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,all the therapies can heal people.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.97,1:42:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.60,1:42:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.92,1:42:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.19,1:42:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
