Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.14,1:43:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get any of the message.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.43,1:43:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be out of here by 5?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.89,1:43:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have to be cleared out by 5.30.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.39,1:43:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, like, everyone's gone by 5.30.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.14,1:43:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
